# Technoclub HALL

Peetri 6, Noblessner, Tallinn

Scheduled events

Hall is a modern cultural centre.

It is internationally known as a Mecca for new electronic dance music in the region.

Hall focuses on new electronic dance music, offering guests superb visual and spatial experience and a chance to relax and recharge batteries.

Hall is also known in Tallinn for its great food and drink.

Hall is a source of inspiration where you can enjoying music, dance and socialise.

Facebook: <https://www.facebook.com/halltallinn/>
